Project: AutoCard Marketplace (Greeting Card Platform)
Stack: Next.js 14 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
Database: Supabase (PostgreSQL)
Auth: Supabase Auth (email + Google OAuth)
Payments: Stripe + Stripe Connect + Stripe Tax
Email: Resend
File storage: Supabase Storage (bucket: designs)
Hosting: Vercel

Rules:
- Always use TypeScript, never JavaScript
- Always use App Router (app/ directory), never pages/
- Server components by default; add "use client" only when needed
- Use lib/supabase/server.ts for server-side queries
- Use lib/supabase/client.ts for client-side queries
- Use lib/supabase/admin.ts only in API routes and webhooks
- Tailwind for all styling, no CSS modules
- All Supabase tables: users, creators, designs, contacts,
  contact_events, orders, creator_earnings_ledger, payouts,
  refund_claims, notifications
